":8238,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/15\/ali-ibn-abu-talib-cursed\/","url_meta":{"origin":24651,"position":1},"title":"Ali on Curses: Those who curse others are themselves cursed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 15, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ubayd al-Kindi reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cThose who curse others are themselves cursed.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad 315 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u0646 \u0639\u0628\u064a\u062f \u0627\u0644\u0643\u0646\u062f\u064a \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u200f \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u200f \u0639\u0644\u064a \u0628\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0637\u0627\u0644\u0628 \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0646\u0647\u200f \u0644\u064f\u0639\u0650\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0639\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0646\u064f\u0648\u0646\u064e 315 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062f\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0641\u0631\u062f \u0644\u0644\u0628\u062e\u0627\u0631\u064a \u0628\u0627\u0628\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31704,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/02\/ali-dua-answered-supplication\/","url_meta":{"origin":24651,"position":2},"title":"Ali on Dua: Distance between heaven and earth an answered prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 2, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Maslamah ibn Muharib reported: It was said to Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, \u201cWhat is the distance between heaven and earth?\u201d Ali said, \u201cAn answered prayer.\u201d Source: al-Muja\u0304lasah wa Jawa\u0304hir al-\u2018Ilm 2576 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064e\u063