":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38271,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/09\/28\/allahu-alam\/","url_meta":{"origin":24651,"position":4},"title":"Ali on Ignorance: When to say Allah knows best","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 28, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Razin Abi al-Nu\u2019man reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cWhen you are asked about what you do not know, then flee.\u201d It was said, \u201cO leader of the faithful, how does one flee?\u201d Ali said, \u201cThat you say: Allah knows best.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Da\u0304rimi\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28156,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/salat-al-witr-ahl-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":24651,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Witr prayer recommended, not obligation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ali ibn Abi Talib reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah is numerically odd and He loves what is odd, so perform the Witr prayer, O people of the Quran!\u201d Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cThe Witr\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/24651","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"